                             <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                               <locus from="1" to="73"/>
                               <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2293Sawase">Sawāsǝw-treatise on lexicon and grammar</title>
                               <textLang mainLang="gez" otherLangs="am"/>

                               <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                                   <locus target="#1"/>
                                  <title>On the word <foreign xml:lang="gez">ብሂል፡</foreign>, and on what is sawāsǝw</title>
                                   <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                                   <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡<gap reason="ellipsis" resp="DN"/>፨
                                 ንቀድም፡ በረድኤተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ሎቱ፡ ስብሐት፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨ ብሂል፡ ማለት፡ ማለት፡ ነው፡ ባሕል፡ ማለት፡
                               ማለት፡ ነው፡ ብሂሎት፡ ማለት፡ ማለት፡ ነው፡ <sic resp="DN">ብሂሎታ፡</sic> ባሕሉ፡ ማለቱ፡
                             ብሂሎታ፡ ማለትዋ፡ ብሂሎቶሙ፡ ባሕሎሙ፡ ማለታቸው፤ ብሂሎቶን፡ ባሕሎን፡ ማለታቸው፡ ብሂሎትከ፡ ባሕልከ፡ ማለትህ፡
                           ብሂሎትኪ፡ ባሕልኪ፡ ማለትሺ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="DN"/> ሰዋስው፡ ብሂል፡ መሽጋገሪያ፡
                         መሰላል፡ ፋና፡ መርከብ፡ <gap reason="lost"/>ዊሁ፡ መሸጋገሪያው፡ ሰዋሰዊሃ፡ መሸጋገሪያ<gap reason="illegible"/>መ፡ ብሂል፡ አርባ፡
                       ተንከተም፤ ብ፤ ድልድይ፡</incipit>
                               </msItem>

                               <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                                   <locus from="1r" to="10v">1-20</locus>
                                   <title type="complete">On prepositions <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዲበ፡</foreign>,
                                 <foreign xml:lang="gez">ላዕለ፡</foreign>, <foreign xml:lang="gez">መልዕልተ፡</foreign>;
                               <foreign xml:lang="gez">ታሕተ፡</foreign>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ቅድመ፡</foreign>;
                             <foreign xml:lang="gez">ድኅረ፡</foreign>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ውስጠ፡</foreign>;
                           <foreign xml:lang="gez">የ፡</foreign>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">አምጣነ፡</foreign>, etc.
                           (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ደቂቅ፡ አገባብ፡</foreign>?).</title>
                                   <textLang mainLang="gez" otherLangs="am"/>
                                   <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                     ዲበ፡ ላዕለ፡ መልዕልተ፤ ብ፤ ላይ፡ በላይ፡ ወደላይ፤ መልዕልተ፡ መንበር፡ ነበረ፤ ዘይቤ፤ በዝፋን፡ ላይ፡ ተቀመጠ፡ ማለት፡<pb n="2"/> ነው፡
                                     በመልዕልተ፡ መንበር፡ ወረደ፤ ዘ፤ ከ<sic resp="DN">ዝፋን፡</sic> ላይ፡ ወረደ፡
                                     </incipit>
                                      <note>Not separated from the previous part.
                                     Before the end the writer returns to explanations about <foreign xml:lang="gez">ብሂል፡</foreign> and related words
                                     (<locus from="10r" to="10v"/>, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ንግባእ፡ ኀበ፡ ጥንተ፡ ሰዋስው፡ ብሂለ፡ ሰዋስው፡
                                       ብሂሎተ፡ ሰዋስው፡ ብ፡ የሰዋስው፡ ማለት፡ ሰዋስው፡ ማለት፡ ነው፤ ባህለ፡
                                       መጽሐፍ፡ ብ፡ የመጽሐፍ፡ ማለት፡ ነው፤</foreign>).</note>
                               </msItem>

                               <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3">
                                   <locus from="10v" to="11v">20-22</locus>
                                   <title type="complete">On <foreign xml:lang="gez">qalamāt</foreign> at nouns
                                   and their correspondences in Amharic; explanations concerning prepositions.</title>
                                   <textLang mainLang="gez" otherLangs="am"/>
                                   <incipit xml:lang="gez">ግዕዝ፡ ቀለም፡ የተገናኘ፡ ቀለም፡ እንተ፡ ውስተ፡ ለ፡
                                     በ፡ ይሆናሉ፡ በእግዚአብሔር፡ ንከብር፡
                                     ዘ፡ በእግዚአብሔር፡ እንከብርአለን፡
                                     </incipit>
                               </msItem>

                               <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                                   <locus from="11v" to="21r">20-41</locus>
                                   <title type="complete">Lexicon for the
                                      Creation (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ሰዋስወ፡ ፍጥረት፡</foreign>) divided into parts for each of
                                      the seven days</title>
                                   <textLang mainLang="gez" otherLangs="am"/>
                                   <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                     <hi rend="rubric">እጽሕፍ፡ ሰዋስወ፡ ፍጥረት፡ ዘእሑድ፡</hi><pb n="12r"/> እኁድ፡ ብሂል፡ አንድ፡ ማለት፡ ነው፡
                                     በቀዳሚ፡ ገብረ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ሰማየ፡ ወምድረ፡ ዘይ፡ አስቀድሞ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ሰማይን፡ ወምድርን፡ ፈጠረ፡
                                     </incipit>
                               </msItem>

                               <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                                   <locus from="21r" to="31r">41-61</locus>
                                   <title>Thematic lexicon including such parts as
                                     <foreign xml:lang="gez">ነገረ፡ ንጉሥ፡</foreign>, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ነገረ፡ እስራኤል፡ ወነቢያት፡</foreign>,
                                   <foreign xml:lang="gez">ነገረ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡</foreign>, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ነገረ፡ መርዓዊ፡</foreign>,
                                 <foreign xml:lang="gez">ነገረ፡ ነጋዲ፡</foreign>, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ነገረ፡ ንዋየ፡ ቤት፡</foreign>,
                               <foreign xml:lang="gez">ነገረ፡ ሕማም፡</foreign>,
                             <foreign xml:lang="gez">ነገረ፡ ኍልቍ፡</foreign></title>
                                   <textLang mainLang="gez" otherLangs="am"/>
                               </msItem>

                               <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                                   <locus from="31r" to="32v">61-64</locus>
                                   <title>Lexicon of verbal forms
                                     (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ድርድር፡ እርባን፡</foreign>)</title>
                                   <textLang mainLang="gez" otherLangs="am"/>
                                   <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                     ድርድር፡ እርባን፡ አእመርኩ፡ ብ፡ አወቅሁ፡ አእመርከ፡ ብ፡
                                     አወቅኽ፡ አእመረ፡ አወቀ፡ አእመርክሙ፡ ብ፡ አወቃችሁ፡
                                     </incipit>
                               </msItem>

                               <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                                   <locus from="33r" to="37r">65-73</locus>
                                   <title type="complete" cert="low" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6511Sawasew">Lexicon
                                     of verbs and poetic formulas (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ሰዋስወ፡ ግስ፡</foreign>)</title>
                                   <textLang mainLang="gez" otherLangs="am"/>
                                   <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                   <hi rend="rubric">እጽሕፍ፡ ሰዋስወ፡ <add place="above">ግስ፡</add></hi> ፍኖተ፡ ጼሐ፡ ፍኖተ፡ ተመርሐ፡ በግዓ፡
                                   ዘብሐ፡ ላህመ፡ ጠብሐ፡ ቀሰመ፡ ልሱሐ፡ ሐነጸ፡ ጽርሐ፡ ቀደሰ፡ ርሱሐ፡ ሞጣሕተ፡ ተሞጥሐ፡ ሀብለ፡ አንኃ፡ ቀርነ፡ ነፍሐ፡ ወርቀ፡ አርብሐ፡ ማኅተመ፡ ፈትሐ፡ ዕደዊሁ፡ ሙቁሐነ፡
                                   ፈትሐ፡ ዓለም፡ ረብሐ፡
                                 </incipit>
                                   <note>In terms of structure, similar to <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6511Sawasew">Sawāsǝw-lexicon of verbs and poetic formulas</ref>,
                                 but only a part of the verbs and expressions is the same.</note>
                               </msItem>

